---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Membership"
  description="Learn about our membership-based endocrinology practice and what's included in your care plan."
>
  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">
      About Membership
    </h1>

    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
      Our membership model allows us to limit our patient panel and provide the
      attentive, personalized care that traditional insurance-driven practices
      simply cannot offer. When you become a member, you're joining a practice
      that puts your health first.
    </p>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-accent mb-6">What's Included</h2>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="bg-background-light rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary mb-2">
            Comprehensive Initial Evaluation
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            A thorough 60-90 minute initial consultation to understand your complete
            health history, current concerns, and goals for treatment.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-background-light rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary mb-2">
            Extended Follow-Up Visits
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            30-minute follow-up appointments (not the typical 10-15 minutes) to ensure
            we address all your questions and concerns.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-background-light rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary mb-2">
            Direct Physician Access
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Communicate directly with your endocrinologist via secure messaging, phone,
            or patient portal. No more phone tag with office staff.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-background-light rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary mb-2">
            Same-Day or Next-Day Appointments
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            When urgent issues arise, you won't wait weeks for an appointment. We reserve
            availability for our members' acute needs.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-background-light rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary mb-2">
            Care Coordination
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            We communicate directly with your other healthcare providers to ensure
            seamless, coordinated care across all aspects of your health.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-background-light rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary mb-2">
            Preventive Care Planning
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Proactive health monitoring and personalized prevention strategies to
            help you stay ahead of potential issues.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-accent/10 rounded-lg p-8 mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-accent mb-4">
        How Membership Works
      </h2>
      <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-700">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">1</span>
          <p><strong>Submit an Inquiry:</strong> Fill out our membership inquiry form with your basic information and health concerns.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">2</span>
          <p><strong>Initial Consultation:</strong> We'll contact you to schedule a brief phone call to discuss your needs and ensure we're the right fit.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">3</span>
          <p><strong>Enrollment:</strong> Complete your membership enrollment and schedule your comprehensive initial evaluation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">4</span>
          <p><strong>Begin Your Care:</strong> Start receiving the personalized, attentive endocrine care you deserve.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-accent mb-4">
        Insurance & Payment
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        The membership fee covers your access to enhanced services and direct physician
        communication. We also bill your insurance for covered services like office visits
        and procedures, just like a traditional practice.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        This hybrid approach means you get the benefits of membership-based care while
        still utilizing your insurance benefits for applicable services.
      </p>
    </section>

    <div class="text-center">
      <a
        href="/become-a-member"
        class="inline-block bg-primary hover:bg-primary-dark text-white font-semibold py-3 px-8 rounded-md transition-colors"
      >
        Become a Member
      </a>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
